oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Girls at Martin College
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Group photograph of girls posed in a room at Martin College. Sadie Lee Stenbeck is the girl in the back center. There are pennants and photographs on the wall, and pillows on the floor.
